  "sentences": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Joseph Sterngast.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am born in 1913, 27 of August.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today, I am 81.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Poland, in Krakow.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was born in Krakow, and I went to school in Krakow.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also was educated in Hebrew and Jewish in Krakow.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- my-- I was at home.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were six brothers and two sisters.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, today, I have only one brother left what he lives in Israel.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How big.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was 300,000 population.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "80,000 Jews.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was with my parents till the bar mitzvah.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After, a year after bar mitzvah, my mother passed away, and two years later, my father passed away.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were orphans.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to start to worry about ourselves.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the elderly brothers and sisters, they do a lot for us, the younger-- the younger [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] brothers and the younger-- the younger brothers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the parents, they left our own house.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to live in our own house, and we had a store.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But one of my brothers, he had a printing business.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And me, when I was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 16, I decided to go and to learn a profession.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I went to a school for almost a year to learn as a auto mechanic and auto driver.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What my-- special one sister was not very happy, that it's not the right profession for me, but I did it anyhow.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What I was very happy, what I did, then I find out in the wartime, because this was-- this was the only way that I survived, because I was very well known even at the Germans as a good mechanic, and I was working for them all the time.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then when it started the war, they made a ghetto, not far from the place where I used to live, you know, almost on the same street.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they closed up the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the permission to enter the ghetto was only for the people what they had a profession, and young people, they were able to work for the Germans.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was chosen.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was one of them, between 1,000 of under.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They let in, into the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And right away, I had a job in the Wehrmacht, [NON-ENGLISH] they used to call.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was working there because I was one of the good workers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They put me as one of the responsible ones.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were 103 people used to go out-- that was out of the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we used to walk quite a bit to the place where we were working.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there, they used to give us a slice of bread and something to drink.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's all what we got from them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But the work was hard work.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was over 50 years ago.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The tools, they didn't have those what the people work today.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Everything we had to do with our own hands.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was very hard, you know, to make an overhaul on the big engines, on the diesels, the Mercedes, and the NAG.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So-- but I was working, and they were very satisfied from me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very bitter was the life in ghetto, because--",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, before?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean when the war started or before the war?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, when the war started it was--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war, so I was at home, you know?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As we were orphans, we were all together.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of my oldest brothers, he left for Palestine.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- the-- we, at home, we had to worry, you know, about our life.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How to-- so my sister, she took over the business, and that was the way we made a living.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was grocery and delicatessen.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very much, all the time.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Poland, we always feel a lot of anti-Semitism.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And closer to the war was even much worse.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The main streets, they were closed with a big-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with-- that was a special kind of closing up the ghetto, you know?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] how you call this-- a big door, you know?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only the entrance for the street car.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were allowed to go.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the streets were closed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were-- we-- we did see the street cars or the trucks what were allowed to move there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About what year did this first happen?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This has happened in 1940, end of '40, '41.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- I was very much engaged with sport, special-- you know, we had the club, Maccabee a Jewish club.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to go almost every day, you know, there to-- for exercises.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was with my friends.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, we had bikes.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We start to go on bikes, and then we start to race on bikes.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maccabee, I joined-- I joined, since my childhood, when I was 15, 16 till 20, 21.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to serve the Polish Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the Polish Army--",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1934.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- you know, as a Jew, and I was-- and my health position was very good.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to go wherever they sent me, you know?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was cavalry.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was, because I had my papers that I am a mechanic and a driver, so my chief, the chief, the Major of the [INAUDIBLE] where I was there, he took me right away.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a car, an old one.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I fixed a little bit the car.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was, as a driver, working with him, going whenever he asked for.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even so far we were, you know, in good terms.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He likes me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whenever he used to leave out of town, he gave me the car.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, you just keep the car and you're the responsible one.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the army was very, very hard, you know, in the Polish Army, and special for Jews.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Matter of fact, that-- one of the Jews commit suicide.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, it was so hard because the anti-Semitism was also in the Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But because my boss was a Colonel, this was the main on the all, you know-- in the all [INAUDIBLE].",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was the-- the only one.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But being in one of the special was a Rotemeister.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was inside the one.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But outside was the Colonel.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And because it started that time already that I find out that I did a very smart move that I learned this profession.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's why I was, you know, I would say one only.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What I didn't feel so much, you know, this anti-Semitism.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, when my Colonel used to go out of town, so my Rotemeister, the inside chief, was with his wife and children, he was coming to me, begging me if it's possible I shall take him to the hospital with the children.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that's why I always, even being in the Army, I was a free man.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, whenever I wanted to be at home, even dressed as a soldier, I used to come for, you know, lunch at home, and for the weekends I had free when the Colonel didn't need me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And others, you know, had very, very hard work.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was with horses.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They used to go at night to work in the stables, you know, to clean up from the horses.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I didn't feel it, this, you know, because I was special.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was really like a chosen one.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "For then, that time, somebody, a mechanic, an auto mechanic and a driver, was really, you know, very few.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So that was for three years I was in the Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Army, I got out end of '36, beginning of '37. 1937 I finished.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back home.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wanted to move to Israel, and I had all my papers prepared.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when they find out that I want to move to Palestine-- at that time, it wasn't Israel.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Palestine.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they called me after a year, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] or after two years, they called me back for exercise, again, to the Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I was supposed to go after three years, but they didn't want to let me out.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was because of anti-Semitism.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't want, as a Jew, I should go to-- to Palestine.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even they always used to say, Jews, they belong to Palestine, but if come the time somebody had the possibility to-- to go to Palestine, it was very hard.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they took me to the-- for the exercises, you know, maneuvers.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was there for two months, again, as a driver.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't feel-- remember this was out of town, far away, you know, till after [INAUDIBLE], all the Polish states who used to-- they used to go on the horses.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I used to go with my Colonel in the car, or a motorcycle with a bi-wagon.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then they let me free.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Liberation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I finished, but they didn't let me go.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they start to talk about a war is coming that Hitler started.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People used to run away from Germany.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the-- my brothers and one of the sisters-- because in meantime, one sister left for Palestine.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The brother, he called her out to Palestine.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the sister with the children what was at home, and the bother, married with children, they was begging me, I shouldn't go.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I shouldn't leave them alone at home.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I shall stay with them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I decided I will be with them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a short time, because when Hitler came, you know, the Germans, they closed up everything, and they start to think about the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the rest of my family, they didn't have the chance to go into the ghetto, because their profession, they didn't like.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they didn't give them the permission to be, to live into the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was the only one.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there, they gave me right away a job.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was working there for the Germans.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't feel very hard for me because I used to come in the evening after the work.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was looking for something to eat.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, to go to sleep and to get up early in the morning.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the soldiers, they were waiting for us, and took us out of town when we were working for them, you know, for-- for the Wehrmacht, for this Army, for the German Army.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- you know, it was allowed to go out of town, not in Krakow, far away from Krakow, because they gave them the permission to stay there for few months, because they knew they will get them all together in one place, or ten other places, and they will send them, you know, to kill them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was prepared already, the camps.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were killing the people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they killed my family what were there, you know, out of town you know?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- from the ghetto, before they give-- they decided to kill the people, I didn't know, and I used to run away from the ghetto on a bike.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a bike with me in the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, bicycle.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to visit them, like to say goodbye.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what's gonna be.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they told me I shall come there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is-- they don't see a soldier.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Until the time came, the soldiers came and take all of them, you know, with the children, with everybody.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They put them into the camps, and they-- they burn them, and they kill them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even now, the-- the-- the places where they did it, they are still not covered completely.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You still can find some, you know, leftovers from the killed people.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About Palestine, I knew that I had to work hard in Palestine, because the [INAUDIBLE], they were the-- above the Palestine.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Refugee experiences"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- Palestine belonged, that time, to the-- to the English, you know?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- that-- I wanted to be with my brother and sister there, but then I gave up because it was impossible.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted, before they killed my family, I was-- I wanted to be with them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But like I mentioned, they didn't let them go into the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't have the-- the profession.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the ghetto was finished, they start, again, to liquidate the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941. 1941, because I was in ghetto from 1940, 1941.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they start to liquidate the ghetto because it was a lot of people, too much of them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The liquidation started-- they surrounded the whole ghetto with soldiers, all over.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one can run away.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went into the apartments and they put the people on one place, and they start to kill them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were shooting without stopping, you know, parents with children, with grandparents, women, you know, they were, you know, with-- also, you know, they told it will be a regular life there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the women were pregnant.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they killed everybody.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't look.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they choose because the soldiers came and they said that they needed people what they work for them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from the Wehrmacht, you know, from the Army, from the German Army.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had my 103 people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were some other places where the Jews used to work.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Them they let out.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't kill them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's going to happen because it was early in the morning.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went for the whole day to work.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came back from work, it was completely empty.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a few people only in the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The left over was only the people what were working.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor",
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- That was all in one day that they killed everyone?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was more than one day.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was two days.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they couldn't kill all of them in the ghetto.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were prepared with the big trucks.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used to send them to Auschwitz, and to Bergen-Belsen, to other places, you know, where they used to kill the people.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So not exactly all of them were killed there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they send out.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this-- everything we-- those working people, they knew about that we-- we had, again, some papers from the Army that we are needed still.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Government"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we presume that the end will be that they're going to kill us.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
